data.description: Explore the character of this 960 sq ft home at 1207 North Ave, Metropolis, IL. Original hardwood flooring, though in need of some TLC, adds charm, complemented by new appliances. Small fenced back yard with a detached garage for convenience, this home embodies a blend of classic features and modern comforts in the heart of Metropolis. Most of the exterior updates have been done for you with new storm doors in 2023, new vinyl siding and windows in 2020, new roof in 2022.  Give us a call to make this home yours!
